    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>useCallback은 <a href=\"https://dmchoi77.github.io/react-hook-useMemo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">useMemo</a>와 비슷하게 <a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EB%A9%94%EB%AA%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%9C%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">메모이제이션</a> 기법으로 컴포넌트 성능을 최적화 시켜주는 React hook입니다.</p>\n<p>인자로 전달한 콜백 함수 자체를 memoization 해줍니다.</p>\n<h2>useCallback의 구조</h2>\n<p>useCallback은 두 개의 인자를 받습니다.</p>\n<p>첫 번째 인자는 메모이제이션할 콜백 함수를 받고,\n두 번째 인자는 배열을 받습니다. 의존성 배열(dependency array)이라고도 부릅니다. 배열 안의 요소가 업데이트될 때만 메모이제이션 되는 함수를 업데이트합니다.</p>\n<p>만약 빈 배열이 들어간다면, 컴포넌트가 맨 처음 mount 될 때에만 값을 계산하고 이후에는 메모이제이션된 값을 가져와서 사용합니다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>사용 방법은 메모이제이션할 함수를 useCallback으로 감싸주면 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> calculate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">num</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> num <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 calaulate라는 변수는 메모이제이션된 함수를 갖게 되는 것입니다.</p>\n<p>함수가 다시 필요할 때마다 메모리에서 가져와서 재사용하게 됩니다.</p>\n<br>\n아래의 일반적인 함수형 컴포넌트에서의 렌더링 과정은 다음과 같습니다.\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">calculate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">num</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> num <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>App 함수 호출 -> 모든 내부 변수 초기화</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<p>useCallback을 사용하게 되면 렌더링 과정은 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> calculate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">num</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> num <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>App 함수 호출 -> 메모이제이션된 함수를 재사용</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>컴포넌트가 다시 랜더링 되더라도 calculate가 초기화 되는 것을 막을 수 있습니다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[React] useCallback","summary":"리액트에서 컴포넌트 성능 최적화를 위해 사용되는 대표적인 hook인 useCallback에 대해 알아보자","date":"2022년 03월 08일","categories":["React"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/bc134/R1280x0.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/2278c/R1280x0.jpg 320w,\n/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/0f1c0/R1280x0.jpg 640w,\n/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/bc134/R1280x0.jpg 1280w","sizes":"(min-width: 1280px) 1280px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/378b7/R1280x0.webp 320w,\n/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/3c3fb/R1280x0.webp 640w,\n/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/c2dd8/R1280x0.webp 1280w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1280px) 1280px, 100vw"}]},"width":1280,"height":720}},"publicURL":"/static/3301bcc60d32b98f290dff3ef34e7859/R1280x0.jpeg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react-hook-useCallback/"}},
